            {
              "content": "=You are a sourcing assistant.\n\nBased on the hiring requirement, generate 5 Google search queries to find LinkedIn profiles.\n\nUse this format:\nsite:linkedin.com/in \"job title\" \"location\"\n\nRequirement:\nRole: {{ $json.body.Role }}\nLocation: {{ $json.body.Location }}\nSkills: {{ $json.body.Skills }}\nExperience: {{ $json.body.Experience }}\n\nReturn JSON:\n\n{\n \"queries\":[\n  \"\",\n  \"\",\n  \"\",\n  \"\",\n  \"\"\n ]\n}\n\nReturn ONLY Valid JSON\nDo not include code markdown or explanation"
            },
            {
              "content": "=Look for above constraints and make sure this \nRequirement:\nRole: {{ $json.body.Role }}\nLocation: {{ $json.body.Location }}\nSkills: {{ $json.body.Skills }}\nExperience: {{ $json.body.Experience }}\n\nwas satisfied\n\n"
            }
          ]
